<br />

<br />
Will terrorism Increase because the terrorists are no longer afraid of there countries being invaded?
<br />

<br />
Will terrorism decrease.  Not sure why but alot of democrats seem to think if Bush is out it will happen.
<br />

<br />
Will it not matter.  Evil people will try to blow things up no matter who is in charge.
<br />

<br />
